thread.title_full: Vital Choice reviewed by janai pringle

author: janai pringle
title: janai pringle
text: No glitz, no razzle-dazzle marketing, no promises full of hype -- just the real deal - when fish was fresh and tasted like you had just caught it. Only Vital Choice does all the work. They ship on time, they deliver when promised, and all comes off without a hitch. I'm so happy I found these guys! Give 'em a try and enjoy!
